{
  "stem": "2170.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were taken to this grave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody had to get undressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Ukrainian people were standing and looking from nearby, and grabbing the clothing, whatever they could, from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Down in the grave was one SS man sitting with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had to undress themselves and walk down steps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When they walked down the steps, he was going through with a machine gun and killing them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on the grave-- I'll, I'll tell you later in the story when I'm telling how-- we find it out very soon, right after that, because Ukrainian told us, other people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were still some of them, which was not all murderers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But most of them were collaborating with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So down in the grave was two men standing there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans giving the orders to put bodies in one side of the grave and in the other side, because they wanted-- had a plan that how much is going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The grave will be open, and they were always taken-- they knew that the plan more has to go in over there into that grave.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they had to put the bodies-- some of them were still alive, one on top on the other.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they finished the job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put a white chemical, like to burn against diseases or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They call it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whatever that was, it was a chemical on the bodies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They did not cover the bodies with any ground, so the birds could come and eat their eyes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time when we saw already [? 5 or ?] 6 o'clock, they came and they told us that we will be taken into two houses and stay there overnight.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
